# LogistiQ - Flowchart Alur Penggunaan Website

## 1. Alur Autentikasi

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[Pengguna Mengakses Website] --> B{Sudah Login?}
    B -->|Ya| C{Role Pengguna}
    B -->|Daftar| D[Isi Form Register: Nama, Email, Password]
    D --> E[Akun Dibuat - Role: unassigned]
    E --> F[Redirect ke /pending - Menunggu Penugasan]
    F --> G[Superadmin Assign Role]
    G --> H[Refresh - Redirect ke Dashboard sesuai Role]
    B -->|Login| I[Isi Form Login: Email, Password]
    I --> J{Login Berhasil?}
    J -->|Ya| C
    J -->|Tidak| K[Error Message]
    K --> I

    C -->|Superadmin| L[Dashboard Global]
    C -->|Warehouse Admin| M[Alerts Page]
    C -->|Store Admin| N[Scan Page]
    C -->|Driver| O[Deliveries Page]
```

## 2. Alur Utama Replenishment (Inti Sistem)

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    subgraph "1. Deteksi Alert"
        A1[Warehouse Admin Buka /warehouse/alerts] --> A2[Lihat Card Stok Rendah]
        A2 --> A3{Ada Stok di Bawah Threshold?}
        A3 -->|Ya| A4[Klik Pack a Box]
        A3 -->|Tidak| A5[Dashboard Normal]
    end

    subgraph "2. Packing Box"
        B1[Buka /warehouse/boxes] --> B2[Pilih Tujuan Toko]
        B2 --> B3[Tambah Item + Kuantitas]
        B3 --> B4[Submit - Stok Gudang Berkurang]
        B4 --> B5[QR Code Box Dihasilkan]
        B5 --> B6[Status Box: PACKED]
    end

    subgraph "3. Assign Driver"
        C1[Buka /warehouse/assign] --> C2[Lihat Box Status PACKED]
        C2 --> C3[Pilih Box dengan Checkbox]
        C3 --> C4{Metode Assign?}
        C4 -->|Scan QR Driver| C5[Scan QR Driver via Kamera]
        C4 -->|Manual| C6[Pilih Driver dari Dropdown]
        C5 --> C7[Status Box: ASSIGNED]
        C6 --> C7
    end

    subgraph "4. Driver Pickup"
        D1[Driver Buka /driver di Mobile] --> D2[Lihat Box yang Ditugaskan]
        D2 --> D3[Klik Pick Up]
        D3 --> D4[Status Box: IN_TRANSIT]
        D4 --> D5[Aktifkan Kirim Lokasi GPS]
        D5 --> D6[Lokasi Dikirim Setiap 45 detik]
    end

    subgraph "5. Pengiriman"
        E1[Driver dalam Perjalanan] --> E2[Lokasi Real-time di Map]
        E2 --> E3[Warehouse Admin Pantau di /warehouse/tracking]
        E3 --> E4[Superadmin Pantau di /dashboard]
    end

    subgraph "6. Penerimaan di Toko"
        F1[Store Admin Buka /store/scan] --> F2[Scan QR Box via Kamera]
        F2 --> F3{Validasi QR + Status + Tujuan?}
        F3 -->|Valid| F4[Stok Toko Bertambah Otomatis]
        F3 -->|Invalid| F5[Error - Coba Lagi]
        F4 --> F6[Status Box: DELIVERED]
        F6 --> F7[Handover Log Tercatat]
    end

    subgraph "7. Penyesuaian Stok (Opname)"
        G1[Store Admin Buka /store/stock] --> G2[Toggle Opname Mode]
        G2 --> G3[Edit Kuantitas Stok]
        G3 --> G4[Simpan Perubahan]
        G4 --> G5[Audit Log: Old Value → New Value]
    end

    A4 --> B1
    B6 --> C1
    C7 --> D1
    D6 --> E1
    E4 --> F1
    F7 --> G1
```

## 3. Alur Superadmin

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[Superadmin Login] --> B[/dashboard]
    B --> C[Lihat Stat Cards: Box, Users, Alerts, Utilization]
    B --> D[Lihat Map Real-time: Gudang, Toko, Driver]
    B --> E[Lihat Activity Log]

    A --> F[/admin/users]
    F --> G[Search/Paginate Users]
    G --> H[Assign Role ke User]
    H --> I[Link ke Gudang/Toko]

    A --> J[/admin/items]
    J --> K[CRUD Item Catalog]

    A --> L[/admin/warehouses]
    L --> M[CRUD Gudang]
    M --> N[Set Koordinat via Map Picker]
    M --> O[Atur Kapasitas & Link Toko]

    A --> P[/admin/stores]
    P --> Q[CRUD Toko]

    A --> R[/admin/warehouse-stock]
    R --> S[Pilih Gudang]
    S --> T[Tambah/Edit/Hapus Stok Item]
```

## 4. Alur Driver

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[Driver Login] --> B[/driver]
    B --> C[Lihat Daftar Pengiriman Aktif]
    C --> D{Status Box?}
    D -->|ASSIGNED| E[Klik Pick Up]
    D -->|IN_TRANSIT| F[Lihat Peta & Rute]
    D -->|DELIVERED| G[Riwayat Pengiriman]

    E --> H[Status: IN_TRANSIT]
    H --> I[Aktifkan GPS Tracking]
    I --> J[Lokasi Dikirim Otomatis]
    J --> K[Warehouse Admin Pantau di Map]

    F --> L[Buka Peta Tujuan]
    L --> M[Navigasi ke Toko]

    A --> N[/driver/qr]
    N --> O[Tampilkan QR Code Pribadi]
    O --> P[Warehouse Admin Scan untuk Assign]
```

## 5. Alur Store Admin

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[Store Admin Login] --> B[/store/scan]
    B --> C[Scan QR Box dari Driver]
    C --> D{Valid?}
    D -->|Ya| E[Stok Bertambah Otomatis]
    D -->|Tidak| F[Error - Coba Lagi]
    E --> G[Box Status: DELIVERED]

    A --> H[/store/stock]
    H --> I[Lihat Stok Toko]
    I --> J{Low Stock?}
    J -->|Ya| K[Badge Peringatan]
    J -->|Tidak| L[Stok Normal]
    I --> M[Toggle Opname Mode]
    M --> N[Edit Kuantitas]
    N --> O[Simpan & Log Audit]

    A --> P[/store/history]
    P --> Q[Lihat Box yang Diterima]
    P --> R[Lihat Log Penyesuaian Stok]
```

## 6. Alur Tracking Driver Real-time

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[Driver Aktif] --> B[navigator.geolocation]
    B --> C[Kirim POST /driver-location]
    C --> D[Server Upsert DriverLocation]
    D --> E[Data Tersimpan: coords, speed, heading]

    F[Warehouse Admin] --> G[Buka /warehouse/tracking]
    G --> H[Poll GET /tracking/locations]
    H --> I[Tampilkan Marker di Leaflet Map]
    I --> J[Update Setiap 5 detik]

    K[Superadmin] --> L[Buka /dashboard]
    L --> M[Poll Data Driver]
    M --> N[Tampilkan di Map Global]
```

## 7. Diagram Alur Keseluruhan Sistem

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    subgraph "Input"
        A1[Register/Akun Baru]
        A2[Login]
        A3[Scan QR]
    end

    subgraph "Processing"
        B1[Superadmin: Kelola Users, Items, Gudang, Toko]
        B2[Warehouse Admin: Alert → Pack → Assign]
        B3[Driver: Pick Up → Deliver → GPS]
        B4[Store Admin: Scan → Opname]
    end

    subgraph "Output"
        C1[Dashboard Global]
        C2[Map Real-time]
        C3[Stok Ter-update]
        C4[Handover Log]
        C5[Audit Trail]
    end

    A1 --> B1
    A2 --> B2
    A2 --> B3
    A2 --> B4
    A3 --> B4

    B1 --> C1
    B2 --> C2
    B3 --> C2
    B4 --> C3
    B4 --> C4
    B4 --> C5
    B2 --> C5
```

---

## Keterangan Simbol

| Simbol | Keterangan |
|--------|------------|
| `[ ]` | Proses / Aktivitas |
| `{ }` | Keputusan (Decision) |
| `-->` | Alur ke langkah berikutnya |
| `subgraph` | Grup langkah yang terkait |
| `/path` | Halaman/rute di website |
